Tony Maudsley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tony_Maudsley 0 Tony Maudsley (born 30 January 1968) is an English actor, best known for playing Kenneth DuBeke in the ITV comedy series Benidorm. He also played Graham in The Job Lot Maudsley made his panto debut in 2016 as Dame Trott in Jack and the Beanstalk at the Royal Theatre Nottingham. He returned the year after playing a completely different part - Genie of the Lamp in Aladdin at the Grand Theatre Swansea.
